reviewText: my nephew loves curius george. he watches him on tv almost everyday of the week. on this dvd, back to school, i'm trying to get him excited about going back to school and start preschool. i hope sometime this month, it happens sooner.

reviewText: "Back to School" is yet another George winner!These stories from the PBS series are sure to make children - of all ages - smile.They also make great Christmas and birthday gifts.

reviewText: Be creative, have fun not only as on "Guest Monkey"  but also with shapes in Charkie goes to school.  It is a great educational tool.
